  "description": "A katsu sando is a classic Japanese sandwich made with crispy pork. For our version, you'll swap pork for crispy breaded chicken and pile it into crusty ciabatta with creamy shredded lettuce and tonkatsu sauce (like a Japanese BBQ sauce). Oishii (yum)! ",
